title: im plat3 just had a normal game matched with 4 under level 30s, and againest s5 diamonds and plats
body: how is this happening?????? riot ples fix ur matchmaking

replies.body:
If you were playing a normal then it would be a combination of things. Most people who are usually in norms are playing URF, and most other people are playing ranked. Couple that with the time and there are very few people in normal Q I imagine.

Normal matchmaking is also a bit wonky just generally because of the lack of tier restrictions.
